{"tid":1154160,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[公投] 祝緒丹 VS 劉亦菲","createTime":"2019-05-14T05:56:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-07T14:34:47.000Z","uid":58335,"like":124,"dislike":338,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"15067499de78259be59bdf1acb9586e8c061a4e4","tid":1154160,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T05:56:24.000Z","msg":"本身諗住祝緒丹 VS 陳鈺琪<br />\n但諗諗下兩個係唔同Type<br />\n好難比較<br />\n但祝緒丹 同 劉亦菲都係仙氣女神可以一比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我投祝緒丹<br />\n丹丹有周芷若個種仙氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n特別個楚楚可憐樣<br />\n唔怪得宋青書要做狗公啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都想做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n劉亦菲古裝幾好幾有仙氣<br />\n但時裝麻麻<br />\n<br />\n祝緒丹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n劉亦菲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n祝緒丹<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/LALOAEL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLALOAEL.png&h=6cf6d341&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/cMCEHjN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcMCEHjN.png&h=1eff00a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/cMCEHjN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcMCEHjN.png&h=1eff00a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/YmX1VEJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https